column5: I was over at 5 lakes lodge today and they told me they had a group move their date to august , this leaves an opening for a group in june. I know there are people out there that are looking for dates in june, this is just a heads up for them. I don't know which week it is but give them a call or send them an email to find out if you are interested . I'm not associated with the camp just trying to pass on a possible opportunity for someone.
Very nice gesture for the guys who decided late!
from one of the many good guys on WC.
Looking forward to fishing with you again this year............oh and sharing a beer at Happy Hour is good also!!!!
